We're planting millions of trees every year to help combat climate change. More trees mean more shade for crops, more carbon removed from the atmosphere, higher yields and improved biodiversity and soil health. 🌳🌲🌴 

Visit the link in or bio to discover how we're protecting and restoring forests around the world ⬆️ 

#ClimateAction #Nestlé #NetZero #Forests #Regeneration
